title: Season 3 - 01 Money.Bob Dylan Theme Time Radio Hour
description:
Forgive me if I repeat what I post on my blog here...copy&paste is a wonderful tool, don&#039;t knock it.

Wow. It really is that time again.
I&#039;m just going to sit back and enjoy this... it seems like such a long time since the last show.

Great choice of theme for the first show coming back ... Money.
I would expect the old Pink Floyd track to be in it but I suppose that&#039;s just too predictable eh...? Mind you it seems this is just &#039;Money Part 1&#039; so that could mean that next week or some other future show we will get another show based on the theme of Money. I bet he&#039;ll include the Floyd track on that one. :)
Talking of money... I wonder what bank Bob uses.
